# Amazon-customer-reviews
𝐀𝐦𝐚𝐳𝐨𝐧 𝐂𝐨𝐧𝐬𝐮𝐦𝐞𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐡𝐚𝐯𝐢𝐨𝐫 𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬:

I've recently created a dashboard using a sample dataset of Amazon, and I've used Power BI to create this project, offering a comprehensive glimpse into customer interactions, browsing behaviors, and more within the Amazon environment.



📌𝐎𝐛𝐣𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞

The goal of this dataset is to offer invaluable insights into the behavioral analysis of Amazon's consumers. It aims to provide understanding of customer preferences, shopping habits, and decision-making processes within the Amazon ecosystem.



𝐊𝐞𝐲 𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬

👩‍👧‍👧 Importance of customer reviews: There is very importance of customer reviews by rating. Here I can see that mostly of customers (30.33%) go only on 1 rate and a few customers (6.46%) go on 5 Rate.



🔎 Frequency of purchase time: There are 43.64% customers who engage only few times a week but 12.13% of customers engage multiple times a week.



🌟𝐒𝐞𝐚𝐫𝐜𝐡 𝐏𝐫𝐞𝐟𝐞𝐫𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞𝐬: Mostly of customers (48.87%) search keyboard-based and (36.57%) search to keyword-based call for optimized search functionality.



🛒 𝐂𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝐀𝐛𝐚𝐧𝐝𝐨𝐧𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐠𝐞𝐬: Strategies needed as 214 customers look for better prices and 205 customers change their mind.



😃 𝐒𝐡𝐨𝐩𝐩𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐒𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐬𝐟𝐚𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧: We can see that 33.86% of customers rating their satisfaction as 3 and 33.07% rating it as 2. 



 Service appreciation: Customers appreciate aspects like product recommendations, wide product selection, user-friendly Etc. The mostly of customers (42.62%) appreciate to product recommendations. While a few customers (0.28%) appreciate to quick delivery. 



𝐊𝐞𝐲 𝐑𝐞𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐝𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬

📝Encouraging reviews, maintaining their quality and recognizing engaged reviewers can enhance the overall customer experience and trust in the platform.  

📝Implement advanced search filters, Category products effective and use relevant categories to ensure that customers can easily find the products, they have looking for.

📝Elevate product quality standards and accuracy to meet customer expectations, Regular quality checks and accurate product descriptions can significantly improve customer satisfaction.



Visit my profile for a detailed analysis of the Amazon dashboard. 🌐🛍️
